featured_reviews.review_id:
Alhamdulillah!!!
Good place for ibadah.
Nice people, good atmosphere.
Flexible Prayer Timings.
Every Friday from Moghrib to Ishaa there is weekly meeting (Gasht ka din).
Masjid is open for ibadah from fajr to Ishaa.
Only night time it'll be closed due to security reasons.
